Order Summary（订单信息）
Order Number: <%= order.number %>
Items:        <%= order.total_items %>

============================================================

<% order.line_items.each do |item| %>
Style No (款号)：<%= item.style_number %>
Size (码数):     <%= order.country_code %>-<%= item.size %>
Color（颜色):    <%= item.colour_name %>
Quantity:       <%= item.quantity%>
Factory:        <%= item.factory %>
Delivery Date:  <%= order.projected_delivery_date %>

Customizations:
<% item.customisations.each do |name, image_url| %>
  - <%= name %>
  <% if image_url.present? %>
  - <%= image_url %>
  <% end %>
<% end %>

<% if item.image? %>
Product Image:
<%= item.image_url %>
<% end %>
------------------------------------------------------------
<% end %>

<% if order.customer_notes? %>
Customer Notes: <%= order.customer_notes %>
<% end %>

Customer Details (客人信息)
------------------------------------------------------------
Customer（客人名字): <%= order.name %>
Phone Number（电话): <%= order.phone_number %>
